message.body: Hey disappearing lady. Show tomorrow?
Hey! I'm so glad u texted, I got a new phone and lost your number in the process. I can't go to a show tonight, but letS hang soon!
sounds good! let's be cold weather show buddies again this year
Yes! I'm much less depressed this year
Ha, me too! Beers next week?
Yes for sure..Tuesdays and Thursdays are good for me
Cool, we can figure out what day we're feeling it next week. And i'll even bike to w philly!
Ha, just kidding i guess about being less depressed. More than a year later and my ex can still make me cry over dumb shit. Drinks tomorrow, or soon?
Yikes, that's the way it goes with depression. Can I let u know tomorrow? I need to see how much work I get done tomorrow during the day
Yeah, of course. If not tomorrow let's plan something soon. Need to keep busy to keep from thinking too much :/
Hey, my birthday is tomorrow, I'm going to rays tonight if you want to come out for drinks! Any time after ten
Cool, i'm in dc and not sure if i'll be home tonight, but will stop by if i am. Happy birthday!
Aw, ok, I hope I get to see you! If not, soon!!!
Home,but totally beat and going to bed. Let's make plans happen soon
What are you up to this wknd?
Hey I don't know how I missed your text...this weekend was stupid busy with school stuff anyway. Do you have tgiving plans?
It's cool, suprise out of town friends had me busy all wknd anyway. Going to ny for tgiving, back saturday but i have to work sunday :/
Oh awesome, I was organizing a friends-giving for anyone not leaving town. I will be so much more able to hang out after the 14th, when the semester is ova!
I love friendsgiving! That's what i'm going to ny for.
Yeah! It's so much better than seeing your family, ha. We need to hang soon tho, I want to hear about your life!
School sux!! Want to go out for first Friday next week?
I was just thinking about you! First friday sounds great.
I must have sensed it! The guy I'm dating has an opening a pageant that night, lets get food and drinks in the area
Sounds perfect. What time do you want to meet up?
Meet around six and get dinner and drinks? Then go out from there?
Yes, yes and yes. Can't wait to see you, beautiful meg!
I know! I've missed you!
Hey lady. Still doing ff tonight?
You betcha. I'm not going to be on bike, so can we keep things around pagaent?
And why does it always rain when we hang out?
Ha, because the weather sucks here? Pagaent is on bainbridge?
Yeah, and eighth I think. I'm getting my hair cut on passyunk now and need to run home to change (out of pajamas) but then I am going to be starving. There will be a keg of beer there tonight!
Yaay! I should be home around 6, just have to change and grab my bike. Food at royal?
Yum sounds good! Meet at 7?
Yes!
Sorry running late as usual add fifteen mins!
No worries, i'm running late too!
You the best!
Here!
Almost there!
Where u at?
Smoking outside
I'm glad I got to see you last night xo
I know, me too! We need to hang again soon.
Yeah, let me know if you go to the PowerPoint
Ha, i'm intrigued but i need more details!
Haha, it is self help through humorous PowerPoint! It starts at 8 at 1026.
I want to go!
Awesome!
Fuck this weather! Not sure how heroic i'm feeling tonight.
Yeah eff this, I have too much work to do anyways. We will hang when I'm done w school!
K, good. That makes me feel so much less lame. When is school over? I have become a total champ at venturing to w philly, fyi
Yeah we aren't lame, we went out once this weekend, ha. Last day of classes is Thursday, and then I just have one final next week!
i even went to a show sat! I'm killing it, lady. Going to see forgetters sat, but hit me up friday if you're up to anything fun.
Yeah, we are pretty much on top of the world!
Hey lady, do you know any one that would be able to take a kitty or two? We need to find homes for our guys
Aww, bummer. I don't know anyone offhand, but i'll let you know if i hear anything
Yeah, Ella's handling it well tho. What are you up to this weekend?
Not sure, erin and i are meeting up in a bit. What about you?
Oh good! Have fun. I'm not sure about the weekend, but Ella is going to her gmothers
You should come out! Want me to let you know where we end up?
Not tonight, I mean next weekend!
Ha, gotcha. Let's try to do something then!
Ok! Have fun tonight!

Meg! Hope you had a killer winter break. I'm going to be in your neighborhood saturday day for a haircut and 2 piece fest. Let me know if you are around and we can grab a bite or a beer. Miss you lady!

Hey lady, sorry I didn't get back to you, I wrote a response and thought I sent it, but didn't. Stupid iPhone. I'm on spring break this week if you want to hang out, I would love to go to shows or drink beerz!
Spring break! Going to a show tomorrow and another one thursday. Come out tomorrow! Erin is supposed to come too.
I know, woo!!
That sounds fun, where is it?
This place called jr's, i've never been. It's at like 22nd and passyunk
Oh yeah I've been there. What is happening Thursday?
Thursday is a house show also in south philly. Can't remember where exactly.
I still don't know if Wes is watching Ella tonight or tomorrow night, but whichever night it is, lets hang out!
I just heard from him. Free tonight! Want to meet at jrs or before?
Excellent! Let's meet up before. Maybe a beer at ray's? Show is at 9
Yes! Beer at rays! Seven thirty?
Perfect!
Yes!
Hey, I wanted to check out an installation in west philly at 6:30, is there any chance we could meet someplace closer? Maybe doobies? Jrs is on 23rd also
Yeah, for sure. There is a chance my ex will be there, they do a comedy thing weds so i might want to bail, but i'm pretty sure it starts later. And i love doobies, so lets go.
Oh yikes, yeah we will run out if that happens! Maybe throw a drink on him!
Totally. And let the air out of his bike tires!
Yes!
Still looking like 730? I might be on time for the first time in my life.
Ha I left early so I just got here. I was determined not to be late
Awesome!
Do you have an extra reflector? I forgot my light and my blinky : (
I do not. And my blinky light is pretty much dead. We'll have to be careful.
We r so dangerous!
Home!
I can't believe u went out on a school night u are such a trooper
Oh my god i'm soooo tired!
Totally worth it though. Was super fun.
I can't even imagine.
Yes! Shows and dark bike rides!
I really should have taken my own advice and not drank that last beer
No more beers for meg
You're grounded from beer.
I get all lovey
Who doesn't
The scientist keeps making it worse for me. He told me his ideal living situation with a partner would be separate bedrooms. I was like Me too! 2nd floor!
It's like he's using his science powers to read your mind! I'm glad he contacted you, did you make any plans?
Ha, i buckled and contacted him. We hung out last night. Now he's like texting me about the something valve in my shower.
Why is he texting you about your shower? Is he trying to get you to move in?
Exactly. His diverter valve is probably perfect. That 2nd floor could be all mine!
Dream situation! I would want my own bedroom if I lived with someone too. Sometimes you want to be alone. Your own floor would be best tho! What r u doing this weekend?
I know! I need to tell him somehow that the ways he thinks he'd be a weird boyfriend are actually very appealing. Going to a drag show tomorrow, but no other plans. You?
Haha, right..he's so used to feeling like a weirdo he doesn't know he's perfect
Not sure, at the plant store now!
Rare plants!
Ugh I just spent an uncomfortable amount of money
On plants! Which makes it exciting!
Good think rent isn't due for a few weeks. They are all so beautiful!
Are you caressing them??
I'm rubbing my face in them. The air in the green house was so oxygen rich and pure
I bet. Thinking about greenhouse air makes me want to visit morris arboretum
Oh yes! Next weekend I want to do the bike ride to valley forge if you are up for it
I want to! I think i have to work on sun so shoot for sat?
Yes! Active healthy lifestyles!
Summer of moderation? Dare i say it?
Ha, i daren't, after thinking about it. Summer of flirting with moderation!
Fifty fifty moderation sounds good. Moderately moderate. We will take long bike rides and celebrate with beer
Brilliant!
https://airbnb.com/rooms/275029
Incredible!!!
My friend and i are freaking out over how great that place looks
Fifty bucks! Did you see the sloth??
Sloth with baby!
I think it's going to be too cold tomorrow for our bike ride. Should we do something else?
I'm so glad you think so! I was afraid of being a wimp. Can we go roller skating?
Haha, where?! How?! Only if you're prepared to watch me fall. A lot.
The place in Camden has open skate at 7. Maybe?!
Maaaybe. I have to work super early sun so i need to have an early night
So I'm at a bridal shower that I thought was supposed to be tomorrow. Maybe we can go out some night this week?
That's cool. Having a weird hangover day anyway and not feeling awesome. Let's do doobies next week.
Hey lady, what are you up to tonight?
Headed out of town! You're so good at wanting to hang out when i'm away
It's like I can sense it! Where ya goin?
visiting friends who live up by the ny border. Totally need a wknd away from philly. Got all hung up on another flakey dude. Going to see some trees and pet some horses and get my mind right!
Good! That sounds amazing! Is the scientist a bust?
Scientist is a bust. Met a cute old punk guy who used to be in a band i liked, haha! Liked him a lot but he flaked. We awkwardly frequent the same bars. Good timing to get out of town!
Good timing! Dudes are flakes, you will have a better time feeding apples to horses anywayz!
Back in philly, wknd was so nice! When are you free? Let's hang soon
Good! I'm glad you got a break from the Philly harsh. I am in the thick of it this next few weeks at school, but I could maybe go out next week, this week is shot
Study hard! You can do it! I will be your academic cheerleader! All i have on my calendar next week is a show sunday, so get in touch if you end up with some available time. Summer is coming!
Yes! I need a cheer leader, moral is low. Summer is sooo soon...
Summer is now! I've announced it.
Good to know! I've been waiting! This is awesome!
What are you up to this weekend?
Nothing fun..I am trying to get as much work done as possible. May 3 is my last day!
That's so soon!
Not soon enough lady! Can we drink outside that day?!
Duh!! It's going to rule.
Thinking about doing at least part of the val forge ride this wknd. Holler if you're interested and around, lady
I'm going to the union game today, but we get back in south Philly tonight. Want to get drinkz?!
Yes! Have fun! Getting dinner around 6 with my friend but will be around after.
Fun fun fun!!
My plans for the day already ruled, and they just got better!
What are u doing today?!
Bike ride, dinner with buddy, getting an iphone, then possibly drinks with you!
An IPhone!!! Yes!
Joining the 2000's!
Welcome 2 the future
What time is dinner? We are coming back from the game now
We're eating now. Where were you thinking about going?
Dunno. My phone will die. Soon!
Ok. Well let me know where you end up? I could do rays.
I will text from Nates fon!
Cool! Stay in touch
Hey! Porting my number took forever, not sure if you texted. What's going on?
I can't stop thinking about the pie chant! It's haunting me.
I know, it gets deep inside you. I really regret the lack of organized chanting yesterday
It's in my soul. Maybe they have a chant night like how the Phils have Irish night?
If this is true then we need to attend this night. Either way, let me know when you want to check out a game!
